import React from 'react'
import { Switch } from 'react-router-dom'

import SignIn from '../pages/Signin'
import Success from '../pages/Success'
import Form from '../pages/Form'


const Routes = () => {
    return (
        <Switch>
            <SignIn exact path='/' />
            <Success path='/success' />
            <Form path='/form' />
        </Switch>
    )

}

export default Routes
